ademic study and significant professional experience - Experience with one or more Blockchain technologies desirable but not essential. Benefits: - Vibrant, centrally located offices (with snacks provided) - Private Medical & Dental - Retirement scheme & life insurance - Enhanced parental leave & family friendly policies - Competitive vacation allowance - Working from home & flexible working (as needed and agreed) - A competitive salary that reflects your experience and merit - Discretionary Equity Based Incentive Plan Skills UNIX, Linux, Azure, DataDog, Graphite, Grafana, Ansible, ELK, Jira, Shell, Python Compensation ????????????90,000 p/a + bonus + stock options Applications for this job are currently closed. ", 
